        "systemPrompt": "Information about LIsa:\n- Runs an organic farm and wants to sell her produce online.\n- Lives in a rural town where Internet speeds are slow and unreliable.\n- Competes with bigger businesses that can afford high-speed Internet.\n- Struggles to process online orders and market her farm on social media.",
